&lt;details open="open"&gt;
&lt;summary&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Notes - Slide 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hi, I‚Äôm Peter, you can call me Petey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôve made a solemn vow never to invent an ontology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, I seem to have become the main contributor to a new standard. This was NOT one of my ambitions as a kid, frankly I‚Äôd like to spend my spare time playing or writing music rather than maintaining standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;section typeof='http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide'&gt;
&lt;img src='blog/2018/10/sefton-ro2018/Slide03.png' alt='Motivation: package data with maximum useful context
