What ‚Ä¶ format are these files? ‚Ä¶ is the research about?
Where ‚Ä¶ was it collected? ‚Ä¶ is it about? 
Why ‚Ä¶ was it done?  ‚Ä¶ &amp;lt;link to publication&amp;gt;
How ‚Ä¶ were these files created? ‚Ä¶ can I repeat that process? 
' border='1'  width='85%'/&gt;
&lt;details open="open"&gt;
&lt;summary&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Notes - Slide 3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We wanted to be able to show data on the web and distribute it with useful metadata. That means allowing a data packager to anticipate what others (including their future self) might want to do with data, and providing enough detail on data provenance to make that possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;
